":"我係獨派 但我都鐘意華夏文化<br />\n但我又唔反對香港基於華夏文化發展出自己嘅本土文化（例如日本韓國）<br />\n族魂之本就係宗教信仰<br />\n香港嘅本土民間信仰 同台灣本土民間信仰一樣 多數都係拜緊中國神<br />\n但唔妨礙台灣係一個獨立嘅民族國家<br />\n（正如尼泊爾人唔係印度人  都可以拜印度神）<br />\n香港嘅黃大仙 車公應該都算本土信仰<br />\n但你話黃大仙車公係大中華膠 一定反對港獨 我又唔信喇<br />\n或者得閒可以去掉聖杯問一問佢地支唔支持港獨"},{"pid":"3b234bac7b0558b86a39e1431a46a18a04f0e8ba","tid":1882226,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f719c48a4eeab196804fb79eeff078b45dec24","tid":1882226,"uid":35820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3d86624493963c7c7e550df203b2f1d9b557d4f","tid":1882226,"uid":86686,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f7e2c35d12692c9cc27dfc3179119f291073f4c","tid":1882226,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:14:47.000Z","msg":"中華文化=無文化"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:19:05.000Z","msg":"你讀書果陣有冇上過中文堂、中國文化堂？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201201/6b266b2d1493237e55e5a5264369e510.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201201%2F6b266b2d1493237e55e5a5264369e510.JPG&h=be467a82&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:44:47.000Z","msg":"啲弱智中國文化撚又會開始吹奏中文博大精深<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cf13a8dd845960752db7f070eb0e49c1dcd21b","tid":1882226,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f719c48a4eeab196804fb79eeff078b45dec24","tid":1882226,"uid":35820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3d86624493963c7c7e550df203b2f1d9b557d4f","tid":1882226,"uid":86686,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f7e2c35d12692c9cc27dfc3179119f291073f4c","tid":1882226,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:14:47.000Z","msg":"中華文化=無文化"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:19:05.000Z","msg":"你讀書果陣有冇上過中文堂、中國文化堂？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https:/